interpretation: The "safety vest" card represents protection, security, and preparation. This card is a reminder to be cautious and mindful of potential dangers in your surroundings. It suggests that you may need to take extra precautions to ensure your safety and well-being. Trust your instincts and don't be afraid to take measures to safeguard yourself. This card may also indicate the need for a safety net or support system to fall back on during uncertain times. Remember to prioritize your safety and the safety of those around you. Embrace your inner safety officer and take the necessary steps to protect yourself and those you care about.
